                            <label>Effective Date <span class="computed-badge">= Revocation expiry</span></label>
                            <input type="text" readonly id="effectiveDate_${idx}" value="${formatDate(computed.effectiveDate)}" style="background:#e8f3fb; color:#0b4f6c; font-weight:700;">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    ${adea ? `
                    <div class="alert alert-warning" style="margin-top:0.5rem; font-size:0.82rem;">
                        ✅ <strong>ADEA employee:</strong> Verify agreement includes 21-day (or 45-day if group) consideration period, 7-day revocation, § 626(f) disclosure, and written advice to consult counsel. Confirm consideration is in addition to amounts otherwise owed.
                    </div>` : `
                    <div class="alert alert-info" style="margin-top:0.5rem; font-size:0.82rem;">
                        ℹ️ <strong>Under-40 employee:</strong> Remove ADEA/OWBPA provisions from agreement (§§ 2(b)(ii)–(iv) and 6(a)). Replace with 5-business-day review period.
                    </div>`}
                </div>

                <!-- ── SECTION D: Final Pay ── -->
